bilingual.source: You are older and smarter than me.
bilingual.target: 你比我年长也比我聪明。

bilingual.source: She can run faster and jump higher than me.
bilingual.target: 她跑得比我快，跳得比我高。

list.abstract: Than（英[ðæn , ðən]，美[ðæn , ðən]），英语单词，连词，译为比；除…；与其。短语搭配有rather than（而不是）、more than（超过）、less than（小于）。例句为“Young people in Britain are more likely than other Europeans to take illegal drugs.（英国的年轻人比其他欧洲人更有可能服用非法毒品。）” 该单词连词的近义词为immediately、directly，介词的近义词为beyond、without、above。

yingyinNormal.en: Better than Maya? Hey! I'm sorry. Better than Maya?
yingyinNormal.zh: 比玛雅还好吗？嘿！对不起，比玛雅还好吗？

yingyinNormal.en: She's three years younger than me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她比我小3岁呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Brawny? They're bigger than mine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 健壮？比我的还大。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow. You know it better than me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哇，你们唱得比我还好。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that went better than expected.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比预料的情况要好。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah? Is he funnier than me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 喔，是吗？他比我风趣吗？

yingyinNormal.en: It's more complicated than that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 实际情况远比嘴上说得复杂。

yingyinNormal.en: They might be smarter than some people.
yingyinNormal.zh: 海豚可能比某些人聪明。

yingyinNormal.en: It's better than hot, it's binding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 比热辣还辣，是契约"捆绑"。

yingyinNormal.en: And we're growing more than we ever have.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可我们种的比以往还多。

yingyinNormal.en: My mother was more beautiful than his.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的母亲比他的母亲美多了。

yingyinNormal.en: Wow. Your life's even duller than mine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的生活竟然比我的还无聊。

yingyinNormal.en: Mine was worse than that. Well, what happened?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的比你还逊。怎么啦？

yingyinNormal.en: Better than I deserve, most likely. And you?
yingyinNormal.zh: 比我应得的还要好。你呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, it is definitely less than a ballpark.
yingyinNormal.zh: 绝对比一个“棒球场”少。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, that guy's hairier than the chief.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这家伙的体毛比队长的还浓密。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the matter? It's harder than I thought.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了？比我想象中困难。

yingyinNormal.en: She's getting more applause than the president.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她得到的掌声比总统还多。

yingyinNormal.en: Damn it, everyone's better at this than me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈的，大家都比我擅长搞浪漫。

yingyinNormal.en: Weirder than watching his two moms make out?
yingyinNormal.zh: 比看班的两个妈妈亲热还要怪吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: introducing the second element in a comparison

examination_example.sentence: What do you say when you disagree with someone who has more power <highlight>than</highlight> you do?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你不同意比你更有权力的人的观点时，你会怎么说？

examination_example.sentence: For the first time in history more people live in towns <highlight>than</highlight> in the country.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 历史上第一次住在城镇的人比住在农村的人多。

examination_example.sentence: For example, heavier women are less likely to develop calcium deficiency <highlight>than</highlight> thin women.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 例如，相比于苗条的女性，较重的女性更不容易缺钙。

sense_info_list.en: used in expressions introducing an exception or contrast

examination_example.sentence: Do your best to engage coworkers in a genuine, back-and-forth conversation, rather <highlight>than</highlight> prioritizing your own thoughts.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽可能与同事进行一次有来有往的真诚交流，而不是优先考虑你自己的想法。

examination_example.sentence: However, when done too often, this habit can sometimes hurt more <highlight>than</highlight> it helps.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，如果太频繁地这样做，这个习惯有时会弊大于利。

examination_example.sentence: Time, rather <highlight>than</highlight> intention, has given them legitimacy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 赋予它们（诺贝尔奖）合理性的是时间，而不是意图。

examination_example.sentence: In France, quality of life is much more important <highlight>than</highlight> efficiency (效率).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在法国，生活质量比效率重要得多。

examination_example.sentence: As I told my parents at dinner that first night, it was all a little more high-pressure <highlight>than</highlight> I'd expected .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 正如我在第一晚的晚餐上告诉父母的那样，压力比我预想的要大一点。

word_usage.usage:
（1）用在rather,sooner等词之后，表示“与其……不如（宁愿）”：
She would rather die than give in.
她宁死不屈。

（2）用于hardly,scarcely和barely之后，表示“刚……就”：
We had hardly/scarcely/barely reached there than/when it began to rain.
我们刚到那儿就下雨了。

（3）用于no sooner之后，表示“（时间）一…就”：
No sooner had the game begun than it started raining.
=The game had no sooner begun than it started raining.
比赛一开始就下起了雨。

word_level_phrase_info.brief_definition: 比以往；比以前；比以往都

sense_info_list.zh: (用于引出比较的第二部分)比

examination_example.sentence: Its output is much higher <highlight>than</highlight> common kinds of rice.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它的产量比普通大米高得多。

examination_example.sentence: Although people liked him a lot, they also treated him much differently <highlight>than</highlight> other people.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 尽管人们非常喜欢他，但他们对待他的方式也与其他人相比大不相同。

examination_example.sentence: For those who value work more <highlight>than</highlight> sleep,  they should listen to what a famous person once said．
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于那些比睡眠重视工作的人来说，他们应该听听一位名人曾经说过的话。

word_usage.usage:
than是比较级的标志，有than的句子一定含有比较的意味。
如：I’m older than her. 
我比她年龄大。（牛津）
